name: BizTalkBusinessLeaders
0:
”Alexa, ask biztalk leaders to start playing”
”play”
”start playback”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: biztalk leaders
Developer Terms of Use
des:
BizTalk leaders is a continuous feed of in-depth interviews with CEOs, entrepreneurs and startup leaders shaking up traditional industries.
Get inspired and informed listening to real life experiences from industry experts as they describe trailblazing and disrupting new paths to successful commercial enterprises.
Learn about the latest products, technological innovations and secrets to success from enterprising pioneers! 
To get started, enable the BizTalk Leaders skill and say, Alexa, Open BizTalk Leaders.' 
Navigate with instructions such as 'Alexa, Next' - 'Alexa, Previous' - 'Alexa, Pause' - 'Alexa, Resume.'
